articles.title: SpaceX launches the 100th mission of the year from Florida's Space Coast (video) - Yahoo! Tech
articles.description: SpaceX launched 29 of its Starlink internet satellites tonight (Nov. 20), on the 100th mission of the year to take off from Florida's Space Coast.
